1] n = ab+bc+ca where n > a > b > c > 0.
2] c > 0, b > 1, and a > 2.
3] b + c > 2 and bc > 1.
4] (n / 3) > a, as if a >= n / 3 then a(b + c) > 3a >= n and ab + ac + bc >= n + bc > n.
5] (Also, since n > 3a and a >= 3, n > 9.)

a, b, c cannot be positive integers not listed here. Thus, 168 is idoneal.
169 is not idoneal; 16*9 + 9*1 + 1*16 = 144 + 9 + 16 = 169.
170 is not idoneal; 10*8 + 8*5 + 5*10 = 80 + 40 + 50 = 170.
171 is not idoneal; 12*9 + 9*3 + 3*12 = 108 + 27 + 36 = 171.
172 is not idoneal; 10*7 + 7*6 + 6*10 = 70 + 42 + 60 = 172.
173 is not idoneal; 11*10 + 10*3 + 3*11 = 110 + 30 + 33 = 173.
174 is not idoneal; 9*8 + 8*6 + 6*9 = 72 + 48 + 54 = 174.
175 is not idoneal; 15*10 + 10*1 + 1*15 = 150 + 10 + 15 = 175.
176 is not idoneal; 12*8 + 8*4 + 4*12 = 96 + 32 + 48 = 176.
177 is idoneal. See the top of this file for a simple proof that 9 < a <= n/3 for any a.

a, b, c cannot be positive integers not listed here. Thus, 177 is idoneal.
178 is not idoneal; 12*11 + 11*2 + 2*12 = 132 + 22 + 24 = 178.
179 is not idoneal; 11*9 + 9*4 + 4*11 = 99 + 36 + 44 = 179.
180 is not idoneal; 18*6 + 6*3 + 3*18 = 108 + 18 + 54 = 180.
181 is not idoneal; 13*12 + 12*1 + 1*13 = 156 + 12 + 13 = 181.
182 is not idoneal; 14*7 + 7*4 + 4*14 = 98 + 28 + 56 = 182.
183 is not idoneal; 11*8 + 8*5 + 5*11 = 88 + 40 + 55 = 183.
184 is not idoneal; 14*6 + 6*5 + 5*14 = 84 + 30 + 70 = 184.
185 is not idoneal; 10*9 + 9*5 + 5*10 = 90 + 45 + 50 = 185.
186 is not idoneal; 12*10 + 10*3 + 3*12 = 120 + 30 + 36 = 186.
187 is not idoneal; 25*4 + 4*3 + 3*25 = 100 + 12 + 75 = 187.
188 is not idoneal; 10*8 + 8*6 + 6*10 = 80 + 48 + 60 = 188.
189 is not idoneal; 15*8 + 8*3 + 3*15 = 120 + 24 + 45 = 189.
190 is idoneal. See the top of this file for a simple proof that 9 < a <= n/3 for any a.

a, b, c cannot be positive integers not listed here. Thus, 190 is idoneal.
191 is not idoneal; 9*8 + 8*7 + 7*9 = 72 + 56 + 63 = 191.
192 is not idoneal; 12*9 + 9*4 + 4*12 = 108 + 36 + 48 = 192.
193 is not idoneal; 15*7 + 7*4 + 4*15 = 105 + 28 + 60 = 193.

206 is not idoneal; 10*8 + 8*7 + 7*10 = 80 + 56 + 70 = 206.
207 is not idoneal; 15*9 + 9*3 + 3*15 = 135 + 27 + 45 = 207.
208 is not idoneal; 12*10 + 10*4 + 4*12 = 120 + 40 + 48 = 208.
209 is not idoneal; 13*8 + 8*5 + 5*13 = 104 + 40 + 65 = 209.
210 is idoneal. See the top of this file for a simple proof that 9 < a <= n/3 for any a.

a, b, c cannot be positive integers not listed here. Thus, 210 is idoneal.

a, b, c cannot be positive integers not listed here. Thus, 232 is idoneal.
233 is not idoneal; 17*12 + 12*1 + 1*17 = 204 + 12 + 17 = 233.
234 is not idoneal; 12*9 + 9*6 + 6*12 = 108 + 54 + 72 = 234.
235 is not idoneal; 15*8 + 8*5 + 5*15 = 120 + 40 + 75 = 235.
236 is not idoneal; 11*10 + 10*6 + 6*11 = 110 + 60 + 66 = 236.
237 is not idoneal; 15*7 + 7*6 + 6*15 = 105 + 42 + 90 = 237.
238 is not idoneal; 16*10 + 10*3 + 3*16 = 160 + 30 + 48 = 238.
239 is not idoneal; 11*9 + 9*7 + 7*11 = 99 + 63 + 77 = 239.
240 is idoneal. See the top of this file for a simple proof that 9 < a <= n/3 for any a.

a, b, c cannot be positive integers not listed here. Thus, 240 is idoneal.
241 is not idoneal; 14*9 + 9*5 + 5*14 = 126 + 45 + 70 = 241.
242 is not idoneal; 10*9 + 9*8 + 8*10 = 90 + 72 + 80 = 242.
243 is not idoneal; 15*11 + 11*3 + 3*15 = 165 + 33 + 45 = 243.
244 is not idoneal; 14*8 + 8*6 + 6*14 = 112 + 48 + 84 = 244.
245 is not idoneal; 13*10 + 10*5 + 5*13 = 130 + 50 + 65 = 245.
246 is not idoneal; 14*12 + 12*3 + 3*14 = 168 + 36 + 42 = 246.
247 is not idoneal; 12*11 + 11*5 + 5*12 = 132 + 55 + 60 = 247.
248 is not idoneal; 16*8 + 8*5 + 5*16 = 128 + 40 + 80 = 248.
249 is not idoneal; 13*9 + 9*6 + 6*13 = 117 + 54 + 78 = 249.
250 is not idoneal; 15*10 + 10*4 + 4*15 = 150 + 40 + 60 = 250.
251 is not idoneal; 13*8 + 8*7 + 7*13 = 104 + 56 + 91 = 251.
252 is not idoneal; 12*10 + 10*6 + 6*12 = 120 + 60 + 72 = 252.
253 is idoneal. See the top of this file for a simple proof that 9 < a <= n/3 for any a.

273 is idoneal. See the top of this file for a simple proof that 9 < a <= n/3 for any a.

a, b, c cannot be positive integers not listed here. Thus, 273 is idoneal.
274 is not idoneal; 12*10 + 10*7 + 7*12 = 120 + 70 + 84 = 274.
275 is not idoneal; 15*10 + 10*5 + 5*15 = 150 + 50 + 75 = 275.
276 is not idoneal; 12*9 + 9*8 + 8*12 = 108 + 72 + 96 = 276.
277 is not idoneal; 19*10 + 10*3 + 3*19 = 190 + 30 + 57 = 277.
278 is not idoneal; 11*10 + 10*8 + 8*11 = 110 + 80 + 88 = 278.
279 is not idoneal; 14*11 + 11*5 + 5*14 = 154 + 55 + 70 = 279.
280 is idoneal. See the top of this file for a simple proof that 9 < a <= n/3 for any a.

a = 93, b = 2, c = 1, ab + bc + ca = 186 + 2 + 93 = 281.
a, b, c cannot be positive integers not listed here. Thus, 280 is idoneal.
281 is not idoneal; 13*12 + 12*5 + 5*13 = 156 + 60 + 65 = 281.
282 is not idoneal; 20*11 + 11*2 + 2*20 = 220 + 22 + 40 = 282.
283 is not idoneal; 17*9 + 9*5 + 5*17 = 153 + 45 + 85 = 283.
284 is not idoneal; 14*10 + 10*6 + 6*14 = 140 + 60 + 84 = 284.
285 is not idoneal; 18*11 + 11*3 + 3*18 = 198 + 33 + 54 = 285.
286 is not idoneal; 17*8 + 8*6 + 6*17 = 136 + 48 + 102 = 286.
287 is not idoneal; 13*11 + 11*6 + 6*13 = 143 + 66 + 78 = 287.
288 is not idoneal; 15*12 + 12*4 + 4*15 = 180 + 48 + 60 = 288.
289 is not idoneal; 19*7 + 7*6 + 6*19 = 133 + 42 + 114 = 289.
290 is not idoneal; 14*13 + 13*4 + 4*14 = 182 + 52 + 56 = 290.

a, b, c cannot be positive integers not listed here. Thus, 312 is idoneal.
313 is not idoneal; 20*11 + 11*3 + 3*20 = 220 + 33 + 60 = 313.
314 is not idoneal; 13*10 + 10*8 + 8*13 = 130 + 80 + 104 = 314.
315 is not idoneal; 15*12 + 12*5 + 5*15 = 180 + 60 + 75 = 315.
316 is not idoneal; 12*11 + 11*8 + 8*12 = 132 + 88 + 96 = 316.
317 is not idoneal; 14*13 + 13*5 + 5*14 = 182 + 65 + 70 = 317.
318 is not idoneal; 12*10 + 10*9 + 9*12 = 120 + 90 + 108 = 318.
319 is not idoneal; 16*9 + 9*7 + 7*16 = 144 + 63 + 112 = 319.
320 is not idoneal; 17*12 + 12*4 + 4*17 = 204 + 48 + 68 = 320.
321 is not idoneal; 15*11 + 11*6 + 6*15 = 165 + 66 + 90 = 321.
322 is not idoneal; 18*16 + 16*1 + 1*18 = 288 + 16 + 18 = 322.
323 is not idoneal; 24*7 + 7*5 + 5*24 = 168 + 35 + 120 = 323.
324 is not idoneal; 14*12 + 12*6 + 6*14 = 168 + 72 + 84 = 324.
325 is not idoneal; 15*10 + 10*7 + 7*15 = 150 + 70 + 105 = 325.
326 is not idoneal; 15*14 + 14*4 + 4*15 = 210 + 56 + 60 = 326.
327 is not idoneal; 15*9 + 9*8 + 8*15 = 135 + 72 + 120 = 327.
328 is not idoneal; 20*8 + 8*6 + 6*20 = 160 + 48 + 120 = 328.
329 is not idoneal; 14*11 + 11*7 + 7*14 = 154 + 77 + 98 = 329.
330 is idoneal. See the top of this file for a simple proof that 9 < a <= n/3 for any a.

339 is not idoneal; 12*11 + 11*9 + 9*12 = 132 + 99 + 108 = 339.

341 is not idoneal; 17*13 + 13*4 + 4*17 = 221 + 52 + 68 = 341.
342 is not idoneal; 15*12 + 12*6 + 6*15 = 180 + 72 + 90 = 342.
343 is not idoneal; 18*11 + 11*5 + 5*18 = 198 + 55 + 90 = 343.
344 is not idoneal; 14*13 + 13*6 + 6*14 = 182 + 78 + 84 = 344.
345 is idoneal. See the top of this file for a simple proof that 9 < a <= n/3 for any a.

a = 114, b = 2, c = 1, ab + bc + ca = 228 + 2 + 114 = 344.
a = 115, b = 2, c = 1, ab + bc + ca = 230 + 2 + 115 = 347.
a, b, c cannot be positive integers not listed here. Thus, 345 is idoneal.
346 is not idoneal; 23*12 + 12*2 + 2*23 = 276 + 24 + 46 = 346.
347 is not idoneal; 15*11 + 11*7 + 7*15 = 165 + 77 + 105 = 347.
348 is not idoneal; 18*10 + 10*6 + 6*18 = 180 + 60 + 108 = 348.
349 is not idoneal; 17*12 + 12*5 + 5*17 = 204 + 60 + 85 = 349.
350 is not idoneal; 14*12 + 12*7 + 7*14 = 168 + 84 + 98 = 350.
351 is not idoneal; 17*15 + 15*3 + 3*17 = 255 + 45 + 51 = 351.
352 is not idoneal; 19*12 + 12*4 + 4*19 = 228 + 48 + 76 = 352.
353 is not idoneal; 16*13 + 13*5 + 5*16 = 208 + 65 + 80 = 353.
354 is not idoneal; 14*11 + 11*8 + 8*14 = 154 + 88 + 112 = 354.
355 is not idoneal; 15*14 + 14*5 + 5*15 = 210 + 70 + 75 = 355.
356 is not idoneal; 13*12 + 12*8 + 8*13 = 156 + 96 + 104 = 356.
357 is idoneal. See the top of this file for a simple proof that 9 < a <= n/3 for any a.

a, b, c cannot be positive integers not listed here. Thus, 385 is idoneal.
386 is not idoneal; 17*10 + 10*8 + 8*17 = 170 + 80 + 136 = 386.
387 is not idoneal; 19*15 + 15*3 + 3*19 = 285 + 45 + 57 = 387.
388 is not idoneal; 16*12 + 12*7 + 7*16 = 192 + 84 + 112 = 388.
389 is not idoneal; 18*13 + 13*5 + 5*18 = 234 + 65 + 90 = 389.
390 is not idoneal; 18*16 + 16*3 + 3*18 = 288 + 48 + 54 = 390.
391 is not idoneal; 15*13 + 13*7 + 7*15 = 195 + 91 + 105 = 391.
392 is not idoneal; 16*11 + 11*8 + 8*16 = 176 + 88 + 128 = 392.
393 is not idoneal; 17*14 + 14*5 + 5*17 = 238 + 70 + 85 = 393.
394 is not idoneal; 16*10 + 10*9 + 9*16 = 160 + 90 + 144 = 394.
395 is not idoneal; 16*15 + 15*5 + 5*16 = 240 + 75 + 80 = 395.
396 is not idoneal; 15*12 + 12*8 + 8*15 = 180 + 96 + 120 = 396.
397 is not idoneal; 26*11 + 11*3 + 3*26 = 286 + 33 + 78 = 397.
398 is not idoneal; 14*13 + 13*8 + 8*14 = 182 + 104 + 112 = 398.
399 is not idoneal; 15*11 + 11*9 + 9*15 = 165 + 99 + 135 = 399.

401 is not idoneal; 17*13 + 13*6 + 6*17 = 221 + 78 + 102 = 401.
402 is not idoneal; 14*12 + 12*9 + 9*14 = 168 + 108 + 126 = 402.
403 is not idoneal; 35*9 + 9*2 + 2*35 = 315 + 18 + 70 = 403.
404 is not idoneal; 14*11 + 11*10 + 10*14 = 154 + 110 + 140 = 404.
405 is not idoneal; 20*15 + 15*3 + 3*20 = 300 + 45 + 60 = 405.
406 is not idoneal; 13*12 + 12*10 + 10*13 = 156 + 120 + 130 = 406.
407 is not idoneal; 17*12 + 12*7 + 7*17 = 204 + 84 + 119 = 407.
408 is idoneal. See the top of this file for a simple proof that 9 < a <= n/3 for any a.

a, b, c cannot be positive integers not listed here. Thus, 408 is idoneal.
